quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  104,1,WOE BETIDE every back-biting slanderer
  104,2,who amasses riches and sedulously hoards them
  104,3,thinking his wealth will render him immortal
  104,4,By no means! He shall be flung into the Destroying Flame
  104,5,Would that you knew what the Destroying Flame is like
  104,6,It is God‘s own kindled fire
  104,7,which will rise up to the hearts
  104,8,It will close in upon them
  104,9,in towering columns